\c 5
\s Umqulu wencwadi ondizayo
\p
\v 1 Ngasengiphenduka, ngaphakamisa amehlo ami, ngabona, khangela-ke, umqulu ondizayo\x + Josh. 3.11.\x*.
\v 2 Yasisithi kimi: Ubonani? Ngasengisithi: Ngibona umqulu ondizayo; ubude bawo buzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, lobubanzi bawo izingalo ezilitshumi.
\v 3 Yasisithi kimi: Lesi yisiqalekiso esiphumela ebusweni bomhlaba wonke\x + Jer. 29.18; Mal. 4.6.\x*. Ngoba wonke owebayo\x + Eks. 20.15.\x* uzaqunywa\x + Isa. 3.26.\x* nganeno mayelana laso\x + Hez. 2.10.\x*, laye wonke ofungayo\x + Tshu. 9.2; Eks. 20.7; Zek.5.4.\x* uzaqunywa\x + Isa. 3.26.\x* ngale mayelana laso\x + Hez. 2.10.\x*.
\v 4 Ngizasikhupha, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, ukuthi singene endlini yesela lasendlini yalowo ofunga\x + Tshu. 9.2; Eks. 20.7; Zek.5.4.\x*\x + Levi 19.12; 8.17; Mal. 3.5.\x* amanga ngebizo lami\x + Levi 19.12; 8.17; Mal. 3.5.\x*; sihlale phakathi kwendlu yakhe\x + Zaga 3.33.\x*, siyiqede kanye lezigodo zayo lamatshe ayo\x + Levi 14.45.\x*.
\s Owesifazana phakathi kwe-efa
\p
\v 5 Ingilosi eyayikhuluma lami yasiphuma\x + 1.19.\x*, yathi kimi: Phakamisa amehlo akho khathesi, ubone ukuthi kuyini lokhu okuphumayo.
\v 6 Ngasengisithi: Kuyini? Yasisithi: Lokhu kuyi-efa ephumayo\x + Hez. 45.11.\x*. Yathi futhi: Lesi yisimo sabo elizweni lonke\x + 1 Sam. 16.7.\x*.
\v 7 Khangela-ke, kwaphakanyiswa isisibekelo somnuso; njalo lo wayengowesifazana owayehlezi phakathi \w kwe-efa\w**\x + Eks. 38.25.\x*.
\v 8 Yasisithi: Lokhu kuyibubi; yasimphosa ngaphakathi kwe-efa; yasiphosa isisindo somnuso emlonyeni walo\x + 4.10.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Ngasengiphakamisa amehlo ami, ngabona, khangela-ke, kwaphuma abesifazana ababili, lomoya wawusempikweni zabo; ngoba babelezimpiko\x + Hos. 4.19.\x* njengezimpiko zengabuzane\x + Jobe 39.13.\x*. Basebephakamisa i-efa phakathi komhlaba lamazulu.
\v 10 Ngasengisithi kuyo\x + Jobe 39.13.\x* ingilosi eyayikhuluma lami: Balithwalela ngaphi i-efa\x + Josh. 3.11.\x*?
\v 11 Yasisithi kimi: Ukumakhela indlu elizweni leShinari\x + Gen. 11.2.\x*; njalo izamiswa ibekwe lapho phezu kwesisekelo sakhe.
